"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-01-Olympic-spirit-unites-the-world-1vG77G9fqiA-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Cartoon  Copied  The 33rd Summer Olympic Games are underway in Paris, France, uniting people from all around the world. The Olympic spirit represents mutual understanding, friendship, unity, and fair competition. It acts as a bridge, bringing together people from all over the world and fostering respect, tolerance and understanding.  (To submit cartoons and share\\u00a0story ideas or\\u00a0feedback on ourcartoon page, please contact us atcartoon_opinions@cgtn.com)  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"